om-and-its-pieces-may-have-landed-in-cape-cod-bay-180988869/</guid></item><item><title>沥青是今年在密苏里州乔普林举行的世界街头绘画节的画布，该节旨在纪念 66 号公路 100 周年</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/asphalt-is-the-canvas-for-this-years-world-street-painting-festival-in-joplin-missouri-which-honors-100-years-of-route-66-180988868/</link><description>沉浸式画作具有巨大的视错觉效果，向“母亲之路”及其对美国文化的影响致敬</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 17:30:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/asphalt-is-the-canvas-for-this-years-world-street-painting-festival-in-joplin-missouri-which-honors-100-years-of-route-66-180988868/</guid></item><item><title>杀虫剂能吸引蚊子吗？实验室昆虫发现避蚊胺的气味会让它们吃到美味佳肴</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/could-bug-spray-attract-mosquitoes-lab-insects-learned-that-the-smell-of-deet-would-lead-them-to-a-tasty-treat-180988866/</link><description>研究人员不知道这些发现如何与现实世界的环境重叠。但研究结果表明，当驱虫剂失效时，我们最容易受到伤害，这意味着我们应该定期重新使用它</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/could-bug-spray-attract-mosquitoes-lab-insects-learned-that-the-smell-of-deet-would-lead-them-to-a-tasty-treat-180988866/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和法国文化将在首尔新现代和当代艺术博物馆交汇</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/korean-and-french-culture-are-set-to-rendezvous-at-a-new-museum-in-seoul-for-modern-and-contemporary-art-180988864/</link><description>蓬皮杜韩华艺术中心是日益壮大的全球艺术博物馆网络的最新成员，将首次举办欧洲立体主义和韩国艺术展览</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 19:01:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/korean-and-french-culture-are-set-to-rendezvous-at-a-new-museum-in-seoul-for-modern-and-contemporary-art-180988864/</guid></item><item><title>四只稀有的关岛翠鸟雏鸟在弗吉尼亚州的设施中孵化，为少量已灭绝的野生鸟类增添了“极其宝贵”的资源</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/four-rare-guam-kingfisher-chicks-hatch-at-virginia-facility-making-an-incredibly-valuable-addition-to-the-small-population-of-