.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/using-colorful-kibble-artists-turn-mona-lisa-the-scream-and-the-kiss-into-museum-masterpieces-that-mans-best-friend-can-appreciate-180988860/</guid></item><item><title>希尔玛·阿夫·克林特 (Hilma af Klint) 是一位相信超凡脱俗的灵魂告诉她要画什么的神秘主义者。现在，她被认为是历史上第一位抽象艺术家之一</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/meet-hilma-af-klint-the-occultist-who-believed-otherworldly-spirits-told-her-what-to-paint-now-shes-considered-one-of-historys-first-abstract-artists-180988859/</link><description>这位瑞典画家早在 1906 年就创作了大胆、充满活力的作品，比瓦西里·康定斯基等同时代人早了几年。法国举办的新展览庆祝她的“圣殿绘画”系列</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 16:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/meet-hilma-af-klint-the-occultist-who-believed-otherworldly-spirits-told-her-what-to-paint-now-shes-considered-one-of-historys-first-abstract-artists-180988859/</guid></item><item><title>霸王龙和其他可怕的掠食性恐龙拥有很小的手臂。科学家可能终于找到了原因</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/tyrannosaurus-rex-and-other-terrifying-predatory-dinosaurs-had-itty-bitty-arms-scientists-may-have-finally-figured-out-why-180988803/</link><description>一项新的研究表明，某些兽脚亚目恐龙（两足，大多数是食肉恐龙）的前肢缩小，作为其坚固头骨的进化权衡</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 15:53:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/tyrannosaurus-rex-and-other-terrifying-predatory-dinosaurs-had-itty-bitty-arms-scientists-may-have-finally-figured-out-why-180988803/</guid></item><item><title>请参阅下周在美国 250 岁生日之前发行的纪念托马斯·杰斐逊和《独立宣言》的新季度</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-new-quarter-honoring-thomas-jefferson-and-the-declaration-of-independence-that-enters-circulation-next-week-ahead-of-americas-250th-birthday-180988843/</link><description>该设计是几种硬币面额之一，也是五枚新 25 枚硬币中的第三枚，专为该国五十周年纪念而设计</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 15:46:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-the-new-quarter-honoring-thomas-jefferson-and-the-declaration-of-indepen